name: Summoning Millions of Gods Daily, My Strength Equals Theirs Combined
summary: [Congratulations, Host, on successfully transmigrating. Your new identity is Aurek XVI, Emperor of the Crossbridge Empire.]Great! Finally, I can experience what it feels like to be an emperor.[Reminder: The Crossbridge Empire is one of the countless empires on the continent of Eura. Your predecessor was Aurek XVI, Intelligence: Imbecile.][Warning: The Crossbridge Empire is on the verge of collapse. Current number of hostile royal factions: 17. Total number of enemies: 7 million. Empire collapse countdown: 1 year.]??[Congratulations, Host, you have awakened the Supreme Summon System! Please actively earn points. Summoned warriors can be elevated to God Rank!]???…Many years later,On the peak of the Holy Snow Mountain, before the Gates of the Divine Kingdom,A tall, slender figure appeared before the guardian angels.The angels soared into the sky, three pairs of flame-wrought wings unleashing a world-ending blaze.“Stop! Ahead lies the Divine Kingdom—this is not a place where mere mortals may tread!”The figure did not raise his head. Instead, with the scepter in his hand, he gently tapped the ground.In an instant, warriors numbering in the billions emerged upon Holy Snow Mountain, each radiating an aura surpassing even that of God Rank.You lifted your head ever so slightly, gazing upon the being that once existed only in myth:“Now, the true conquest begins.”
author: Cancer_Reo
